=head1 DESCRIPTION

Within the prepaid payment model defined under
C<ConfigurableUpfrontPricingTerm>, the C<RateCardItem> defines all the
various rate cards (including pricing and dimensions) that have been
proposed.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Constraints => L<Paws::MarketplaceAgreement::Constraints>

Defines limits on how the term can be configured by acceptors.


=head2 RateCard => ArrayRef[L<Paws::MarketplaceAgreement::RateCardItem>]

Defines the per unit rates for product dimensions.


=head2 Selector => L<Paws::MarketplaceAgreement::Selector>

Differentiates between the mutually exclusive rate cards in the same
pricing term to be selected by the buyer.



